body: Never has murder seemed so erotic.
I check everyday for up"DATES", and it finally paid off.

No it's either a bad translation or attempt at a rewrite. In that panel Slime-chan says "kanojo-teki" （彼女的）or girlfriend-like and not "kare-teki"（彼的）which would be "boyfriend-like" (https://nhentai.net/g/261376/3/). I bet there'll be a reupload soon correcting this.

So are there two males and one female, or do they just identify as male while in the body of a female? Does the slime multiply and make new bodies that act independently or are they controlled? I have so many questions and am so curious. Good work though, hope the main man (Yuuji) gets a good ending.
Thank you for the update and will continue to wait for future updates ^_^
